              <div class="p-3 shadow-sm rounded-5 border bg-white">
                  <h2 class="h5 mb-3 text-center">For Renters</h2>
                  <img src="https://png.pngtree.com/png-clipart/20200701/original/pngtree-searching-buy-and-rent-car-flat-illustration-png-image_5426813.jpg"
                    alt="Car Renter" class="img-fluid mb-3">
                  <p class="small text-center">Looking for a car to rent? Find a variety of vehicles that suit your needs and budget, all in one place.</p>
                  <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
